# Fisa_clienti

## Application description

Fisa_clienti is a clients CLI application written in Python that uses SQLite as a persistence engine.

## Usage

### Setting up the virtual environment

```
 $> python -m venv .venv
```

### Activating the virtual environment

#### On Windows based systems

```
 $> .venv\Scripts\activate
```

#### On Unix based systems

```
 $> source .venv/bin/activate
```

### Installing dependencies

```
 $> python -m pip install -r requirements.txt
```


### Deactivating the virtual environment

```
 $> deactivate
```

## Testing

```
 &> python -m unittest
```

## Project structure

### `database.py`

This is the module used to handle SQLite connections and data manipulations for the persistence layer.